<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mislike2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mislike,</orth> vb. to dislike, to disapprove: <cit><quote>m. me not for my complexion,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.1.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 1, 1</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>'tis not my speeches that you do m.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.140" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 140</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if he m. my speech and what is done,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.147" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 147</bibl></cit>.
